    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>This foul smelling potion will quickly heal&nbsp;</em><em>serious injury and even help curtail other minor afflictions.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-style: normal;\">Minor Action:&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Drink this potion and spend a healing surge. You do not regain hit points as normal. Instead,&nbsp;</span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-style: normal;\">regain <strong>25 </strong></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-style: normal;\">hit points a</span></em></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">nd make a saving throw against each effect on you that a save can end.</span></p>",
